[19/07/2018 12:40:47] <font color="#00ff00">Me parece una idea excelente,</font>
[19/07/2018 12:40:47] <font color="#00ff00">yankee.</font>
[19/07/2018 12:40:51] <font color="#00ff00">¿Pero y tu pellejo</font>
