[19/07/2018 14:28:08] <font color="#ffffff">-Vale, Tula.</font>
[19/07/2018 14:28:11] <font color="#ffffff">-Estamos agarrando a su cría</font>
[19/07/2018 14:28:13] <font color="#ffffff">y querrá</font>
