[19/07/2018 19:31:04] <font color="#ffff00">¿El quebequés?</font>
[19/07/2018 19:31:04] <font color="#ffffff">Eso es.</font>
[19/07/2018 19:31:06] <font color="#ffff00">La anfitriona nos da permiso</font>
