[19/07/2018 21:30:33] <font color="#00ff00">falta la indispensable,</font>
[19/07/2018 21:30:38] <font color="#00ff00">Meryl Streep, porque su ausencia era</font>
[19/07/2018 21:30:38] <font color="#00ff00">algo insalvable.</font>
